title: The Latest: Kardashian, brothel owner spar over Odom media
text: > Top News The Latest: Kardashian, brothel owner spar over Odom media Richard Hunter, media director for Dennis Hof, who owns the Love Ranch, talks, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015 in Crystal, Nev., about how he found former NBA basketball player Lamar Odom unconscious the day before. Odom, the NBA star and reality TV personality embraced by teammates and fans for his humble approach to fame, was on life support Wednesday, his estranged wife Khloe Kardashian by his side. Odom was found unresponsive after four days at the brothel. (AP Photo/Chris Carlson)
